# Flipper-Zero-ESP32-Port

header text

> Supported hardware : lily t-embed cc1101
> kurz erklären um was es hier geht ... die originale flipper zero unleashed firmware wurde so nahe wie möglich kopiert und für die esp32 hardware angepasst, die meisten funktionen sind erfolgreich portiert worden.


features:
- SD-Card ( highly recommend )
- Sub-Ghz
  - Included Protopirate
- Bluetooth
  - Remote App (Qflipper)
  - BLE Spam
  - BLE Walk
  - BLE Clone (dev)
- Wifi
  - Connect to Wifi
  - Deauth
  - Handshake sniffer
  - Packet sniffer
- NFC (need to be tested)
- RFID
- Infrared
